						<summary>

						<p>This registers a gift of land for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Perumānaḍigaḷ at Gōvindapāḍi in Valla-nāḍu by Amudan Peṟṟāḷ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Pallavan-Mādēviyār of Kāṇattūr in Umbaḷa-nāḍu the queen of Śōḻapperumānaḍigaḷ (Parāntaka).</p>						

